fields.Title: KIM SWITCH / KLAASJE REACTION
fields.Description: Kim reacts to you losing your shit (Composure fail) when the Hardie boys said the victim is a young woman called Klaasje in the Whirling-in-Rags.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Try me.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Try me."

fields.Title: You: ""No.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Mhm," he nods. "What else did you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm," he nods. "What else did you do?"

fields.Title: Horrific Necktie: "You'll get through it, you slippery..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You'll get through it, you slippery fuck! Blast some insane-o at him, throw him off.

fields.Title: You: ""Better not to add anything to that.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Better not to add anything to that."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He repeats: "Officer, before we int..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He repeats: "Officer, before we interview this woman -- is there something I should know?"

fields.Title: You: ""That's it." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's it." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Whatever you do, don't say the firs..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Whatever you do, don't say the first thing.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I'm going to assume she overheard..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm going to assume she overheard you -- anything else?"

fields.Title: You: ""I didn't rape her.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't rape her."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He shrugs. "That's clearly your int..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He shrugs. "That's clearly your interrogation technique. Anything else?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Is there something I should know b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is there something I should know before we talk to her?"

fields.Title: You: ""I asked her where we are, what cit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I asked her where we are, what city is this, maybe even *what year*. Something like that."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You'll get through it."
fields.Dialogue Text: You'll get through it.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "His opinion of you has lowered cons..."
fields.Dialogue Text: His opinion of you has lowered considerably.

fields.Title: Drama: "'Tis art."
fields.Dialogue Text: 'Tis art.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The victim? Is there something I s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The victim? Is there something I should know before we talk to her?"

fields.Title: You: ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: Half Light: "Ice is forming on the inside of you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ice is forming on the inside of your chest cavity, cold sweat trickles down your neck...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Okay," he nods. "That's manageable.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay," he nods. "That's manageable."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Wonderful. I'm going to assume she..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wonderful. I'm going to assume she overheard you -- anything else?"

fields.Title: You: ""What was what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What was what?"

fields.Title: You: ""I think I know that woman.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think I know that woman."

fields.Title: You: ""She knows I did some pretty crazy..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She knows I did some pretty crazy stuff before I passed out. That I partied hard. And not very mental-healthily."

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "You feel fortified by his assurance..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You feel fortified by his assurance. It's going to be all right.

fields.Title: You: ""She said I'm going to have to inte..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She said I'm going to have to interrogate her later and it's going to *suck* for me."

fields.Title: You: ""And the... sort of... quivering je..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "And the... sort of... quivering jello thing with the eye?" (Point to your twitching eye.)

fields.Title: You: "Not very fun."
fields.Dialogue Text: Not very fun.

fields.Title: You: ""It's an art thing. You wouldn't un..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's an art thing. You wouldn't understand."

fields.Title: You: ""I tried to hit on her...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I tried to hit on her..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Understood." He's stone-faced."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Understood." He's stone-faced.

fields.Title: You: ""It went pretty okay, I guess.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It went pretty okay, I guess."

fields.Title: You: ""You mean the sweating and the fidg..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You mean the sweating and the fidgeting when he mentioned her name?"

fields.Title: You: ""I met her. In the hallway, after I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I met her. In the hallway, after I woke up."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "So this is what it feels like to be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: So this is what it feels like to be *interviewed*...

fields.Title: You: "Fun."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fun.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm not going to answer that, lieu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not going to answer that, lieutenant."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Then don't *ever* say that again."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Then don't *ever* say that again." There's a pause.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Anything else?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anything else?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""So she overheard you? Or did you *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So she overheard you? Or did you *party* together?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Anything else?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anything else?"

fields.Title: You: "I got nothing to hide."
fields.Dialogue Text: I got nothing to hide.

fields.Title: Authority: "He's not leaving you a lot of room..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's not leaving you a lot of room to back off from this.

fields.Title: Horrific Necktie: "Of course it is, you slippery fuck!..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course it is, you slippery fuck! Blast some insane-o at him, throw him off.

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: ""I think I know that woman.""]
Kim Kitsuragi: ""What you're saying is..." he says..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What you're saying is..." he says in a low, calm voice. "*You* raped her?"

fields.Title: You: ""She overheard me listening to musi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She overheard me listening to music and doing weird things. From her room. It's the one next to yours."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "I wouldn't say it is."
fields.Dialogue Text: I wouldn't say it is.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You looked strange when he mention..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You looked strange when he mentioned the assault victim's name." He looks you in the eye: "Do you know that woman?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""This is unprofessional." He repeat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is unprofessional." He repeats: "Not sharing information with me is *unprofessional*."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It doesn't matter how it *went* of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It doesn't matter how it *went* officer -- what else?"

fields.Title: You: ""It was nothing.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It was nothing."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's not nothing, you were coming..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's not nothing, you were coming apart at the seams." He looks you in the eye: "Do you know the assault victim?"

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "What if you do -- but you just don'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What if you do -- but you just don't *remember* that you do?

fields.Title: You: ""No.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Understood -- you were not in good..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Understood -- you were not in good shape on Monday."

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah, we partied all right. Partie..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, we partied all right. Partied all night like the Inzany Boys."

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Is it, though? 'Nothing'? You're st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Is it, though? 'Nothing'? You're still in for a bumpy ride here, try not to mess it up.

fields.Title: You: ""She knows I didn't remember being..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She knows I didn't remember being a cop."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It *is*," he nods. "This would hav..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It *is*," he nods. "This would have been good to know *before*."

fields.Title: You: ""It didn't come up.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It didn't come up."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It should have. Anything else?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It should have. Anything else?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What else?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What else?"

fields.Title: You: ""Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He nods. "We'll be all right, offic..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He nods. "We'll be all right, officer. This is nothing."
fields.Alternate1: "We'll be all right, lieutenant. This is nothing."
